<P>Now this Statute, I am humbly of Opinion, is directly in the Negative, which &s;ays. That for the future nothing &s;hall be adjudged Trea&s;on, other|wi&s;e than it was ordained by the afore&s;aid Statute 25 Edw. 3</P>
