<P><HI>March 11.</HI> The Commi&s;&s;ioners met, and the Pri&s;oner brought to the Bar. Mr. <HI>Nicoll</HI> offered the following Rea&s;ons.</P>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Nicoll</SPEAKER>
<P>It does not appear that any one Overt Act, alledged in the In|dictment, has been proved by the Oaths of two lawful Witne&s;&s;es, as by the Statute of 7 <HI>W<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">.</HI> 3. ought to be done.</P>
